Package: alderIPMSim
Title: Decision Support for the Alnus-Beetle-Parasitoid-Bird Ecoepidemic System
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person('Sinchan', 'Ghosh', role = c('aut', 'cre'), email = 'gsinchanpostdoc@gmail.com')
URL: https://github.com/gsinchanpostdoc/alder-ipm-sim, https://gsinchanpostdoc.github.io/alder-ipm-sim/
BugReports: https://github.com/gsinchanpostdoc/alder-ipm-sim/issues
Description: Simulate, fit, and analyze the hybrid seasonal-annual ecoepidemic model
    for Alnus glutinosa forests. Detect early warning signals of regime shifts,
    evaluate integrated pest management strategies, and forecast ecosystem
    trajectories.
